You will write readable code, create meaningful tests, and participate in code reviews that emphasize clarity and long term maintainability. Success in this position includes designing robust architecture, monitoring with actionable alerts, and reducing operational toil. Candidates should demonstrate practical experience with postgres, sql, microservices, python, asyncio and a willingness to learn additional tools as needed. Our team values end to end ownership, thoughtful trade offs, and an iterative approach to shipping features safely. Exposure to security, performance tuning, and capacity planning is considered a plus, alongside mentoring less experienced teammates. Daily work involves collaborating with product managers and designers to translate requirements into production features. The role focuses on building scalable services and improving developer productivity through automation and clear documentation. We expect strong communication, structured problem solving, and an ability to explain decisions with measurable impact. We are seeking a backend engineer to design, implement, and maintain reliable systems.

job_text: You will write readable code, create meaningful tests, and participate in code reviews that emphasize clarity and long term maintainability. We are seeking a mobile engineer to design, implement, and maintain reliable systems. Success in this position includes designing robust architecture, monitoring with actionable alerts, and reducing operational toil. The position offers opportunities to influence technical direction and to collaborate across functions while respecting realistic deadlines. We expect strong communication, structured problem solving, and an ability to explain decisions with measurable impact. Our team values end to end ownership, thoughtful trade offs, and an iterative approach to shipping features safely. Daily work involves collaborating with product managers and designers to translate requirements into production features. Candidates should demonstrate practical experience with ios, swift, kotlin, appstore, push and a willingness to learn additional tools as needed. Exposure to security, performance tuning, and capacity planning is considered a plus, alongside mentoring less experienced teammates. The role focuses on building scalable services and improving developer productivity through automation and clear documentation. You will write readable code, create meaningful tests, and participate in code reviews that emphasize clarity and long term maintainability.
